## Files to know

- `mkdocs.yml`  
  Main documentation site (Marimo-first tutorials and narrative docs).

- `mkdocs-api-ref.yml`  
  API reference site (auto-generated).

- `docs_scripts/gen_ref_pages.py`  
  Generates API Markdown pages and `SUMMARY.md`.

- `docs_scripts/hooks.py`  
  Minimal cleanup and TOC pruning for generated API pages.

- `serve.py`  
  Builds both sites, merges them, and either serves locally or writes to `site/` with `--build-only`.